snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine’s daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, Kíla Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX® in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection - Official Physical Edition Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the latest Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection trailer for the fighting game compilation to see the announcement from Digital Eclipse and Atari that physical editions are coming, as revealed during EVO 2025. Physical editions of Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection will include Standard, Deluxe, and Kollector’s Editions. Additionally, Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection will also include the return of Mortal Kombat Trilogy, the 1996 entry that brought every playable character from the 2D Mortal Kombat series into one single game.

Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection will be available on PlayStation 5 (PS5), PlayStation 4 (PS4), Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PC via Steam, Nintendo Switch 2, and Nintendo Switch in 2025. Physical versions of the game will be available on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, PC, Nintendo Switch 2, and Nintendo Switch.

#MortalKombatLegacyKollection #Gaming #IGN

Physical versions of the game will be available on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, PC, Nintendo Switch 2, and Nintendo Switch.

snippet.title: Pasta - Dareyes de la Sierra (Video Oficial)
snippet.description:
•ESCUCHA AQUÍ “Pasta”
https://orcd.co/pastadareyes

•LETRA
La cabeza yo nunca la agacho
Ni para abrocharme los zapatos
Tamos bendecidos como quiera
Dios me libre de gente culera

Las calles me dieron mi diploma
Y ahora navego mi mamalona
A mi lado siempre una nalgona
Carita de barbie pero cabrona

La cabeza yo nunca la agacho
Ni para ajustarme los zapatos
Tamos bendecidos como quiera
Dios me libre de gente culera

Y Ahora traigo pasta
Prendo uno de mostaza
Pa fumar con la raza
Las plebitas tiran wasap
Que les caiga pal cantón
Por qué quieren ver acción
Aguardiente y lavadón
Tequila, caguama, champaña
Y tusita bubalo

Buena ta la loquera
Bueno ta el ondeadón
Pinche gente Culera
Que habla y sin razón
Inhalo y exalo
Y saco lo malo

Y a los que me critican
Ja, ja neta dan risa
Wacha esa nalguita
Que rica mamacita

Me pinteaba la escuela de morro
Y con los plebes me echaba un Porro
El estudio nunca fue mi rollo
Pero yo supe salir del hoyo

Pal trabajo yo nunca me rajo
Pero también me gusta el relajo
San juditas siempre me ilumina
Ya es viernes vamos por unas Frias

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Pa’ que la nena resbale
Solo tiene puesto el tanning debajo del traje
Ella es dulce como el matcha con agave
Pero a veces lo de bicha se le sale

Cuando le explota la nota y te pide más
Se fue pa’ no volver pero ella es un boomerang
Una gatúbela está marca’ por la maldad
Te la encuentras por la “Cerra”, ahí como si nada hubiera pasao’
Y eso me gusta a mí
Pero soy el hijo’e puta mami que te gusta ti yeah,
Ya yo le he dao’, encharca’ yo la vi
es Rauw Alejandro

Si quieres verme no pongas pero
El problema no es sentir
Es quién lo dice primero
Tú eres bipolar, yo soy medio grosero
Vamo’ a destrozar la casa, acabar en el suelo
Hasta llegar a buenos

Términos, términos
Se vino el splash y aquí encima terminó
Terminó, terminó
En cuatro le prendí el flash y más se inclinó
Buenos términos, buenos términos
Te viniste…
Dime cuándo no
Dime cuándo no, cuándo no
Peleamo’ y nos comemo’ y queda en buenos términos

(Ra Rauw Alejandro)
(Ra Rauw)
Me dice me escapo…
(Dímelo Ninow, yeah)
Me dice me…

snippet.title: Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A new tale of Riders and monsters takes flight! Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection, the next evolution of the turn-based, story-rich RPG series, is coming to Nintendo Switch 2, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC/Steam in 2026. 

Twin Rathalos, born in a twist of fate, ignite the long dormant flames of war between two fractured nations: Azuria and Vermeil. You are the heir to the kingdom of Azuria, and the sole Rathalos Rider in the kingdom. On the brink of war and amidst strange phenomena threatening the world, a life changing event propels you beyond the Meridian, and on an unforgettable journey in search of the truth. 

Learn more:
https://www.monsterhunter.com/stories3/

snippet.title: Dax - "Man I Used To Be" (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
[LYRICS BELOW] "Man I Used To Be" is a personal song i wrote. Share this with everyone and anyone and let's make an impact. Somebody out there needs this. Love y'all...Thank you.

Click here to listen:  https://dax.lnk.to/TheManIUsedToBe


Follow DAX: @ thatsdax
Shot by: Logan Meis
Produced by: Jimmy Robbins


#ManIUsedToBe #Dax #recovery #masculinity #addiction #sober #manhood


LYRICS:

I’m half the man I used to be 
It’s gon’ take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you’re up all you do is fall
And that’s why I’m
Half the man I used to be

Trials and tribulations 
All my past trauma
Generational curses from daddy and mama
Heartbreak and lies
Dirty soul ties 
Mixed with addictions that clouded my eyes
I’ve been mistaken and taken for granted
and locked in the prison that I call my mind
And now that I’ve lived and I’ve learned  
And I’ve built and I’ve burned all these bridges I’ll leave it behind
And that’s why

I’m half the man I used to be 
It’s gon’ take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you’re up all you do is fall
And that’s why I’m
Half the man I used to be

Don’t ask the reason I changed
Ask yourself why you stayed the same 
I couldn’t sleep in that bed I made
I needed more in life 
I tried every remedy prescribed 
Getting drunk every night 
Letting women waste my time 
Now I’m in a phase I can sleep alone 
I don’t ever chase, I got God
Letting go of pain that was never mine
Trying to bear the weights 
not my job 
Cause that’s the man i used to be
And he ain't no use to me

I’m half the man I used to be 
It’s gon’ take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you’re up all you do is fall
And that’s why I’m
Half the man I used to be

I’m half the man I used to be 
It’s gon’ take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you’re up all you do is fall
And that’s why I’m
Half the man I used to be

______________________________________________________

If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. This is our first new release of 2025 and the first song I've ever released under complete prolonged clarity. This year will have my best and most impactful work. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. This is music for the PEOPLE, spread BY THE PEOPLE. Like, comment, SHARE and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world.

Official Video for “Man I Used To Be" by Dax

스파이더맨: 새로운 시작 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lCmqSbnYfo0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB

새로운 슈퍼맨 2 발표, 개봉일, 다른 주요 캐릭터들과의 슈퍼맨 팀업, 슈퍼걸, 저스티스 리그 저스티스 갱 캐릭터, 새로운 빌런, 브레이니악 설명. 첫 번째 슈퍼맨 2025 영화의 줄거리와 줄거리의 허점.

슈퍼맨 2025 이스터 에그, 배트맨에게 무슨 일이 일어났나, 슈퍼맨 배트맨 월드 파이니스트 티저, 슈퍼맨 2 속편 영화, 영화 전체의 이스터 에그 및 참고 자료. 반달 새비지, 포스트 크레딧 장면, 엔딩 설명. 밀리 알콕의 슈퍼걸 장면. 새로운 슈퍼맨 대 헨리 카빌의 슈퍼맨 변화. 제임스 건의 새로운 저스티스 리그. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드, 브래들리 쿠퍼 조엘 카메오 장면, 켈렉스 로봇, 새로운 장면. 새로운 배트맨 변화와 배트맨을 위한 DC 영화 계획 설명. 새로운 영상과 장면. 포트리스 오브 솔리튜드. 슈퍼맨 대 울트라맨, 사악한 슈퍼맨. 그린 랜턴 첫 등장. 미스터 테리픽 크립토 장면. 슈퍼맨 대 렉스 루터, 새로운 영상, 슈퍼맨 레거시 2025 티저. 새로운 슈퍼맨 슈트, 플래시 리턴즈 설명. 밀리 알콕의 슈퍼걸. 새로운 슈퍼걸 대 이전 버전. 슈퍼걸 우먼 오브 투모로우 영화 티저. 데이비드 코렌스웨트 슈퍼맨, 니콜라스 홀트의 렉스 루터 설명, 맨 오브 스틸, 배트맨 대 슈퍼맨, 저스티스 리그와 같은 이전 버전의 렉스 루터와의 변화. 어쏘리티. 슈퍼맨 레거시 줄거리와 스토리 설명. 새로운 슈퍼걸 설명.

배트맨 브레이브 앤 더 볼드 티저와 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 배트맨 브레이브 앤 더 볼드 티저와 새로운 배트맨은 내년에 발표될 예정입니다. 네이선 필리언의 그린 랜턴, 호크걸, 미스터 테리픽 등 새로운 저스티스 리그 캐릭터들. 뉴 저스티스 리그가 애니메이션 저스티스 리그 팀에 더 기반을 둔 이유

제이슨 모모아 로보, 헨리 카빌, 슈퍼맨 미래 계획, 배트맨 브레이브, 그리고 대담한 제임스 건 DCEU 리부트 설명. 제임스 건이 저스티스 리그 배우들을 어떻게 재구성하는지. 로버트 패틴슨, 배트맨, 그리고 새로운 제임스 건 DC 영화 계획.

더 많은 DC 및 마블 예고편이 곧 공개됩니다. 슈퍼맨 2 영상, 어벤져스 둠스데이 예고편, 그리고 더 많은 판타스틱 4 영상도 곧 공개됩니다!

『ニュー・スーパーマン2』の発表、公開日、スーパーマンと他の主要キャラクターのチームアップ、スーパーガール、ジャスティス・リーグのジャスティス・ギャングのキャラクター、新たなヴィラン、ブレイニアックの解説。前作『スーパーマン2025』のプロットスレッドとプロットホール。

『スーパーマン2025』のイースターエッグ、バットマンに何が起こったのか、スーパーマン：バットマン・ワールドズ・ファイネスト・ティーザー、続編『スーパーマン2』、映画全体からのイースターエッグと参考資料。ヴァンダル・サベージ、ポストクレジットシーン、エンディング解説。ミリー・アルコックのスーパーガールシーン。『ニュー・スーパーマン』対ヘンリー・カヴィルのスーパーマンの変化。ジェームズ・ガン監督による『ニュー・ジャスティス・リーグ』。孤独の要塞、ブラッドリー・クーパーのジョー＝エルのカメオ出演シーン、ケレックス・ロボット、新シーン。新バットマンの変更点とDC映画におけるバットマンの計画について解説。新映像とシーン。孤独の要塞。スーパーマンvsウルトラマン、邪悪なスーパーマン。グリーン・ランタンの初見映像。ミスター・テリフィックのクリプトシーン。スーパーマンvsレックス・ルーサー、新映像、スーパーマン・レガシー2025のティーザー。新スーパーマンスーツ、ザ・フラッシュ・リターンズの解説。ミリー・アルコックのスーパーガール。新スーパーガールvs旧バージョン。スーパーガール・ウーマン・オブ・トゥモローの映画ティーザー。デヴィッド・コレンスウェットのスーパーマン、ニコラス・ホルトのレックス・ルーサー解説、マン・オブ・スティール、バットマンvsスーパーマン、ジャスティス・リーグなど、旧バージョンのレックス・ルーサーからの変更点。オーソリティ。スーパーマン・レガシーのプロットとストーリー解説。新スーパーガール解説。

バットマン：ブレイブ＆ザ・ボールドのティーザーとニューバットマンは来年発表予定。 『バットマン：ブレイブ・アンド・ザ・ボールド』のティーザーと『ニュー・バットマン』は来年発表予定です。ネイサン・フィリオン演じるグリーンランタン、ホークガール、ミスター・テリフィック、そして新たなジャスティス・リーグのキャラクターが登場。『ニュー・ジャスティス・リーグ』がアニメ版ジャスティス・リーグのチームをベースにしている理由。

ジェイソン・モモア・ロボ。ヘンリー・カヴィル演じるスーパーマンの今後の計画。『バットマン：ブレイブ・アンド・ザ・ボールド』ジェームズ・ガン監督DCEUリブート版について解説。ジェームズ・ガン監督がジャスティス・リーグの俳優陣をリキャストする理由。ロバート・パティンソン演じるバットマンと、ジェームズ・ガン監督のDC新作映画の計画。

DCとマーベルの予告編が続々登場。『スーパーマン2』の動画、アベンジャーズ：ドゥームズデイ予告編、そしてファンタスティック・フォーの動画も近日公開！

hi.description:

नए सुपरमैन 2 की घोषणा, रिलीज़ की तारीख, अन्य बड़े किरदारों के साथ सुपरमैन की टीम, सुपरगर्ल, जस्टिस लीग जस्टिस गैंग के किरदार, नए खलनायक, ब्रेनियाक की व्याख्या। पहली सुपरमैन 2025 फिल्म के कथानक के सूत्र और कथानक की खामियाँ।

सुपरमैन 2025 ईस्टर एग्स, बैटमैन का क्या हुआ, सुपरमैन बैटमैन दुनिया का सबसे बेहतरीन टीज़र, सुपरमैन 2 सीक्वल फिल्म, ईस्टर एग्स और पूरी फिल्म के संदर्भ। वैंडल सैवेज, पोस्ट क्रेडिट सीन, अंत की व्याख्या। मिली एल्कॉक सुपरगर्ल सीन। नया सुपरमैन बनाम हेनरी कैविल सुपरमैन बदलाव। जेम्स गन नई जस्टिस लीग। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ सॉलिट्यूड, ब्रैडली कूपर जोर-एल कैमियो सीन, केलेक्स रोबोट्स, नए सीन। बैटमैन में नए बदलाव और डीसी मूवीज की बैटमैन के लिए योजना की व्याख्या। नए फुटेज और सीन। फोर्ट्रेस ऑफ सॉलिट्यूड। सुपरमैन बनाम अल्ट्रामैन, ईविल सुपरमैन। ग्रीन लैंटर्न फर्स्ट लुक। मिस्टर टेरिफिक क्रिप्टो सीन। सुपरमैन बनाम लेक्स लूथर, नए फुटेज, सुपरमैन लिगेसी 2025 टीज़र। नया सुपरमैन सूट, द फ्लैश रिटर्न्स की व्याख्या। मिली एल्कॉक सुपरगर्ल। नई सुपरगर्ल बनाम पिछले संस्करण। सुपरगर्ल वुमन ऑफ टुमॉरो मूवी का टीज़र। डेविड कोरेंसवेट सुपरमैन, निकोलस हॉल्ट लेक्स लूथर की व्याख्या, लेक्स लूथर के पिछले संस्करणों जैसे मैन ऑफ स्टील, बैटमैन बनाम सुपरमैन, जस्टिस लीग से बदलाव बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड का टीज़र और नए बैटमैन की घोषणा अगले साल की जाएगी। नाथन फ़िलियन, ग्रीन लैंटर्न, हॉकगर्ल, मिस्टर टेरिफिक और कई नए जस्टिस लीग किरदार। नया जस्टिस लीग एनिमेटेड जस्टिस लीग टीम पर ज़्यादा क्यों आधारित है?

जेसन मोमोआ लोबो। हेनरी कैविल, सुपरमैन की भविष्य की योजनाएँ, बैटमैन ब्रेव एंड द बोल्ड, जेम्स गन डीसीईयू रीबूट की व्याख्या। जेम्स गन कैसे जस्टिस लीग के कलाकारों को नए सिरे से चुन रहे हैं। रॉबर्ट पैटिंसन, बैटमैन और जेम्स गन की नई डीसी फिल्म की योजनाएँ।

और भी कई डीसी और मार्वल ट्रेलर आ रहे हैं: सुपरमैन 2 के वीडियो, एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे का ट्रेलर और फैंटास्टिक फोर के और भी वीडियो जल्द ही!

With my Grandpa’s rifle in my hand
Lord just take me as I am
And bury me in bottomland
And bury me in bottomland

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. Edward Scissorhands - https://youtu.be/TKkn-qTDsEM

Titanic 2 - https://youtu.be/9tNWfBoqWrU
------------------------------------------------
🕴  John Wick: Chapter 5

Speculation is swirling online that John Wick: Chapter 5 could be on the horizon, with fan communities buzzing about Keanu Reeves potentially donning the black suit one last time. Though there’s been no formal confirmation from Lionsgate or the actor himself, various breadcrumbs dropped in recent months have reignited hope for a continuation of the legendary assassin’s story.

Following the ambiguous ending of Chapter 4, where Wick is presumed dead — yet suspiciously off-screen — fans have theorized that the Baba Yaga may have faked his death to escape the High Table’s grasp. Some even believe this has been a long game, orchestrated with the Bowery King (Laurence Fishburne), to dismantle the Table from the shadows.

Adding fuel to the fire, director Chad Stahelski recently mentioned in an interview that there are “more stories to be told in the Wick universe,” and fans were quick to point out that the word “chapter” implies an ongoing narrative rather than a definitive ending.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Official Career Deep Dive
snippet.description:
Take control of your Career in FC 26 with all new requested features, inspired by the community. Pre-order FC 26 now: https://x.ea.com/85163

For a more in depth breakdown check out the Pitch Notes here: https://x.ea.com/85164

Experience Manager Career like never before with all-new Manager Live Challenges. Take on a variety of real-world scenarios and alternative storylines throughout the new season. snippet.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Be the first to know when we launch! Follow our Indiegogo Pre-Launch Page: [https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/spider-man-alone-episode-1/coming_soon/]

Happy National Spider-Man Day! From Golden Century Films and our "Marvel Inspire" universe, this is the official teaser trailer for 'Spider-Man: Alone.'

'Spider-Man: Alone' is a deeply personal, character-driven fan series that plunges into the heart of Peter Parker's earliest days. A modern, street-level reimagining of Amazing Fantasy #15, our story explores the profound isolation and immense weight of newfound powers. This is the story of a boy learning to fly, and the agonizing, often lonely, process of what it cost him to become a hero.

This project is also proud to launch our Inspired Action initiative in partnership with the non-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, aiming to turn on-screen heroism into real-world change.

Follow the Journey & Join Our Community:
► Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/goldencenturyfilms/]
► Twitter/X: [https://x.com/GoldenCenturyTV?t=nvrx03KCKC60Z4TcAYX5KA&s=09]
► Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/share/1GUwgCDW4o/]

About This Project:
'Spider-Man: Alone' is a non-profit fan film. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Marvel, Sony, or any of their subsidiaries. It is a passion project created by fans, for fans, in celebration of a character who has inspired us our entire lives. The pilot will be available for free.

#SpiderManAlone #FanFilm #SpiderMan #Marvel #Sony #TeaserTrailer #IndieFilm #ComingSoon #StreetLevelSpiderMan #BrandNewDay #SupportIndieFilm #Crowdfunding #NationalSpiderManDay

snippet.title: GOAT - Official Teaser Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
You’re never too small to dream big.

From the studio that brought you Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse and producer Stephen Curry, #GOATmovie is exclusively in movie theatres February 2026.

Visit our site: https://goat.movie/
Find your team: https://theroarleague.com/

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.instagram.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.tiktok.com/@goatmovieofficial
https://x.com/the_goat_movie

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

From Sony Pictures Animation, the studio behind Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse, comes GOAT, an original action-comedy set in an all-animal world. The story follows Will, a small goat with big dreams who gets a once-in-a-lifetime shot to join the pros and play roarball – a high-intensity, co-ed, full-contact sport dominated by the fastest, fiercest animals in the world. Will’s new teammates aren’t thrilled about having a little goat on their roster, but Will is determined to revolutionize the sport and prove once and for all that “smalls can ball!”

Directed by: Tyree Dillihay 

Co-Directed by: Adam Rosette 

Produced by:

snippet.title: This Roblox Scammer Promised to Quit, So I Stalked Him...
snippet.description:
...and it turns out I found him doing something even worse.

ElijahGives is infamously known as Roblox's most desperate scammer, and he told me he was going to quit. So after Elijah promised me to stop scamming kids on roblox, I secretly stalked him and figured out his previous scams and cybercrimes he committed in the past.

And while I thought he gave up scamming because he got relentlessly cyberbullied for being a pathetic scammer, it turns out Elijah's dark past caught up to him and caused even more problems.

snippet.title: Wayward | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Welcome to Tall Pines. We think you’ll be very happy here. Wayward, starring Mae Martin & Toni Collette, premieres September 25, only on Netflix.

More About Wayward: After an escape attempt from an academy for “troubled teens”, two students join forces with a newly local police officer, unearthing the town’s dark and deeply rooted secrets. Wayward stars Mae Martin, Sarah Gadon, Sydney Topliffe, Alyvia Alyn Lind, Brandon Jay McLaren, and Toni Collette.

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. snippet.title: Xavi, Kapo – Bien Pedos (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Escúchala en todas las plataformas: https://BienPedos.lnk.to/XaviXKapo 

Sigue a Xavi: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xaviiiofficiall/ 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@xaviiiofficial 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/xaviiiofficiall 

Sigue a Kapo: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yosoytukapo/ 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@yosoytukapo 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kapooficial/ 

LYRICS / LETRA: 

Bella y sensual, mamacita se le nota que es real,  
sube un story porque hoy sale a pistear,  
Es un culazo, con carita angelical, la baby no tiene rival,  
Y antes que la noche se me acabe y empiece el nuevo día,  
solo quiero hacerte mía.  

Voy a robarte un beso, cuando estemos bien pedos,  
brindamos pa’ arriba pa’ bajo pal centro y pa’ dentro  
La nota por el cielo, la ropa por el suelo, 
brindamos pa’ arriba pa’ bajo pal centro y pa’ dentro. 

Soy fanático de lo que hay en tu interior,  
todo lo que tu traes es un misterio, 
cuando llegaste todo estuvo mejor, 
besitos sabor a tequila mi cielo. 

Y si estás conmigo te ves más guapa te ves más bella, 
si me preguntan por la que me gusta la señalo a ella, 
la veo bailando en la disco danza y se ve coqueta, 
y al salir de aquí, me quedo viendo su silueta. 

Y más yo quiero algo más  
desconocía si ya aquí metida cierra los ojos  

Voy a robarte un beso cuando estemos bien pedos,  
brindamos pa’ arriba pa’ bajo pal centro y pa’ dentro  

La nota por el cielo, la ropa por el suelo  
brindamos pa’ arriba pa’ bajo pal centro y pa’ dentro. 

Tu combinas con la luna y el mar flow natural  
te voy a robar, que tu combinas con la luna y el mar  
oh nanana, oh nanana na 
Que tu combinas con la luna y el mar flow natural  
te voy a robar que tu combinas con la luna y el mar  
oh nanana oh nanana 
Voy a robarte un beso cuando estemos bien pedos. 

#Xavi #Kapo #BienPedos #Bien #Pedos #Fiesta

Written by: Hayley Williams, Daniel James, James Harmon Stack, Eli Teplin

LYRICS:
Tourists stumble down Broadway
Cumberland keeps claiming bodies
All our best memories 
Were bought and then turned into apartments
The club with all the hardcore shows
Now just a greyscale Dominos 
The churches overflow each Sunday greedy Sunday morning 

Gift shop in the lobby
Act like God ain’t watching 
Kill the soul, turn a profit 
What lives on? Southern Gotham

I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
With my belief
And I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
Cause I’m a true believer

They put up chainlink fences underneath the biggest bridges
They pose in Christmas cards with guns as big as all the children
They say that Jesus is the way but then they gave him a white face
So they don’t have to pray to someone they deem lesser than them

The South will not rise again
Til it’s paid for every sin 
Strange fruit, hard bargain
Till the roots, Southern Gotham

I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
With my belief
And I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
Cause I’m a true believer

I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
With my belief
And I’m the one who still loves your ghost
I reanimate your bones 
Cause I’m a true believer

#HayleyWilliams #TrueBeliever

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Lauren Daigle - “Let It Be A Hallelujah” (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
Listen/Stream "Let It Be A Hallelujah" at: LaurenDaigle.lnk.to/LetItBeAHallelujah

Lyrics:
Take my life and let it be  
My soul devoted Lord to Thee 
Take my moments and all my days 
Make them endless praise 
Take my heart and let it move 
In spirit and in truth  
For the glory of Your name  
 
With every breath that's in me  
With every song and melody  
Let it be a hallelujah  
In every breaking moment  
In every blessing that You give 
Let it be a hallelujah  
Oh Lord, let it be a hallelujah 
 
All my hopes and all my fears 
Every trial, every tear

snippet.title: THIS IS NOT SKYRIM 2 - BECOMING A GOD In Tainted Grail A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME
snippet.description:
What Does It Take To Make A God In A Video Game.

The year is 2025 and with bethesda teasing a return to the world of oblivion gamers are once again searching for a taste of skyrim. With the oblivion remaster looking to be a remake that fleshes out some skyrim systems like stealth archer builds I thought it would be a good idea to dive into a new games spin on the RPG formula. This game is Tainted Grail: The Fall of Avalon. It has split news outlets with half saying it is an indie skyrim and half saying its indie dark souls. For me the spiffing brit this game is perfectly balanced. Remember this game is NOT SKYRIM but perhaps just like skyrim we can find infinite money glitches, overpowered magic and an array of silly physics moments. 

If you are interested in the game you can grab it on steam sale here at some point: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1466060/Tainted_Grail_The_Fall_of_Avalon/

It is described as follows: Step into a dark reimagination of Arthurian legends in this first person, open world RPG. Explore a world stuck in everlasting autumn, witness falling legends and make meaningful choices woven into a complex, branching storyline. SO yeah it does indeed hit all of the lovely buzzwords that todd howard used to draw me into the world of tamriel and skyrim all those years ago. So lets hunt for bugs, glitches and exploits in this open world adventure.

00:00 An ode to Bethesda
01:52 I’m a Tod Get me Out of here
04:37 Press Space to Continue 
06:38 Time to Level up
07:59 But Just before I leave

18:10 When a man needs a spell

snippet.title: Starve Away!
snippet.description:
god-sanctioned death
the kind that I like best
I like a good just war
it's what guns are for
I like a good crusade
it brightens my day
starve away!

annihilate
with cosmic vindication
bring us John Wayne justice
for the chosen nation
lord, scatter their bones in your sweetness
speed forth the second coming of the great white Jesus

this is my prayer unto you
oh lord, I hope it comes true
rain down your blessings from heaven on me
and starve the women and the children of my enemy

warranted pain
and holy retribution
couple things my god needs
to make a solution
may their children wander aimless in desolated streets
with no memory of a mother, no father indeed

raised up by war
their fist in a clench
breed the next generation
of bombs in the ditch

this is my prayer unto you
oh lord I hope it comes true

to starve away

down in Arkansas
she says lucky me

snippet.title: Blade: The One and Only | Character Reveal | Marvel Rivals
snippet.description:
🧛 Half human, half vampire, you know his name — Blade. 
 
Almost a century ago, Eric Brooks was born of two worlds: the light of his mother's embrace and the dark of the vampire that attacked her. After embracing his existence as a dhampir, he became the Daywalker, the ultimate vampire hunter, combining unmatched combat skills and unwavering supernatural abilities. 
 
When Dracula reigned over New York City, it was none other than Blade who confronted him first. By then, however, it was too late. Dracula had mastered the almighty power of Chronovium, defeating the Daywalker and imprisoning him within the castle dungeon. 
 
After Dracula's fall, Blade was sent to Wakanda to recover, but his story is far from over. Now recruited by Shuri to save all existence, Blade stands awake and at the ready against the dark forces of Hela and Knull.
 
Only time will tell how this will all unfold, find out more about S3.5 on August 8 UTC. 🗡️
 
Play free now on:
 
🔹 Steam: https://t.co/IPhy0Of1cG
🔹 PlayStation: https://t.co/FR0aVfTmcn

snippet.title: Past Life #4 - Improv is a Blast!
snippet.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.

snippet.title: Spinal Tap - Stonehenge ft. Elton John (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to Stonehenge ft. Elton John out now: https://SpinalTap.lnk.to/Stonehenge
Pre-order The End Continues out September 12: https://SpinalTap.lnk.to/TheEndContinues
 
Follow Spinal Tap: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/spinaltapmovie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/spinaltap
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@spinaltap
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpinalTap/
Website: https://spinaltap.com
 
“The End Continues” is the newest album from Spinal Tap, in conjunction with the forthcoming sequel, ‘Spinal Tap II: The End Continues.’ Both the second film and album are set to release on September 12, 2025. The 13-track album includes new original songs and classics with features from Elton John, Paul McCartney, Garth Brooks and Trisha Yearwood.
 
Forty-one years after the comedy classic ""This is Spinal Tap,"" SPINAL TAP II: THE END CONTINUES reunites director Rob Reiner with Christopher Guest, Michael McKean, and Harry Shearer as they reprise their iconic roles as the legendary heavy metal band Spinal Tap in this long-awaited sequel. Featuring Elton John, Paul McCartney, Garth Brooks, Questlove, and more. Coming to theaters September 12!

#SpinalTap #Stonehenge #TheEndContinues

Pactamos en nunca hablarnos de amor
Quedamos en alejarnos mejor
Me llamas cuando quieras calor
Que seré mejor que el anterior

Disfruto verte en ropa interior
Hacer que tú te vengas toas’ estas veces es un goal

Quiere dulce y yo le doy mi lollypop pop pop pop
Me vuelve loco su chupop pop pop pop
Se moja allá abajo y suena … … ….
Pa tu novio una pistola que hace plop plop plop plop

Ella dice y yo le doy mi lollypop
Pa que ella le de chupop pop pop pop
Se mojo eso allá abajo le sono … … ….
Pa tu novio una pistola que hace plop plop plop plop

Eh eh eh Yo se lo metí y piche
Le di tanto bicho que hasta la embiche
No queria la leche y yo la boca la enleche
Ella queria un polvo y yo como 7 le heche

Es que se lo metí y piche
Le di tanto bicho mierma que hasta la embiche
No quería la leche y yo la boca le enleche
Ella quería un polvo y yo como 7 le heche

Tú te trepas encima de mí y te empiezas a mover
Yo cierro los ojos y no te quiero ver
Tu eres una matemática sin entender
Que la suma es bellaquera hasta el otro nivel

Dale ven aquí que te quiero ver
Ponte en 4 ma’ que te voa’ romper
Tengo ganas de ti y te quiero comer
Yo te tengo mojaitos los pantys chanell

Quiere dulce y yo le doy mi lollypop pop pop pop
Me vuelve loco su chupop pop pop pop
Se moja allá abajo y suena … … ….
Pa tu novio una pistola que hace plop plop plop plop

Ella dice y yo le doy mi lollypop
Pa que ella le de chupop pop pop pop
Se mojo eso allá abajo le sono … … ….
Pa tu novio una pistola que hace plop plop plop plop

Eh eh eh Yo se lo metí y piche
Le di tanto bicho que hasta la embiche
No quería la leche y yo la boca la enleche
Ella quería un polvo y yo como 7 le heche

Es que se lo metí y piche
Le di tanto bicho mierma que hasta la embiche
No quería la leche y yo la boca le enleche
Ella quería un polvo y yo como 7 le heche

La dominican llego con el puertorrican
Las envidiosas toas’ mordías la critican
Ella no tira puya y comoquiera toas’ se pican
Quieren aplicarle, pero no la aplican

Le doy pon pal cielo
Le doy pa’ las uñas, pestañas y el pelo
Yo le di una G Wagon, ella sabe que la quiero
Desde que la opere la Hija e’ puta se cree modelo

Una maniática sexual que le gusta bellaquear
Que cuando empieza no quiere parar
Cuando tu te mueves asi, sabes que se me va a parar
Y tu dices que te mojaste accidental

Mínimo 100 polvos semanal
Cuando yo te pille en 4 mami duro te voa’ dar
Enpercociao la voa’ formar
El desafío tuyo y mío es personal

snippet.title: Cheap Trick - The Flame | 80's Music Greatest Hits - Back To The 1980s | Old Memories
snippet.description:
𓆝 𓆟 𓆞 𓆝 𓆟 Welcome & Thank You for visiting Old Memories Channel.
▶︎ •၊၊||၊|။||||| 19:80s  ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ  ↻ ◁ || ▷ ↺

🎶 Enjoy timeless memory songs
💖 Music to help you relax, reminisce, and embrace romantic moments
🌙 Perfect for peaceful evenings with your loved one

⋆⭒˚｡⋆ 

☾⋆⁺₊🎧🎸✨🌷͙֒  Lyrics: 
[Verse 1]
Another night slowly closes in
And I feel so lonely
Touching heat freezing on my skin
I pretend you still hold me

[Pre-Chorus]
I'm going crazy, I'm losing sleep
I'm in too far, I'm in way too deep over you
I can't believe you're gone
You were the first, you'll be the last

[Chorus]
Wherever you go, I'll be with you
Whatever you want, I'll give it to you
Whenever you need someone
To lay your heart and head upon
Remember after the fire, after all the rain
I will be the flame
I will be the flame

[Verse 2]
Watching shadows move across the wall
Feels so frightening
I wanna run to you, I wanna call
But I've been hit by lightning

[Pre-Chorus]
Just can't stand up for fallin' apart
Can't see through this veil across my heart over you
You'll always be the one
You were the first, you'll be the last

[Chorus]
Wherever you go, I'll be with you
Whatever you want, I'll give it to you
Whenever you need someone
To lay your heart and head upon
Remember after the fire, after all the rain
I will be the flame
I will be the flame

[Guitar Solo]

[Pre-Chorus]
I'm going crazy, I'm losing sleep
I'm in too far, I'm in way too deep over you
You'll always be the one
You were the first, you'll be the last

[Chorus]
Wherever you go, I'll be with you
Whatever you want, I'll give it to you
Whenever you need someone
To lay your heart and head upon
Remember after the fire, after all the rain
I will be the flame
I will be the flame
[Outro]
Whatever you want, I'll give it to you
Wherever you go, I'll be with you
And whatever you want, I'll give it to you
Oh, whatever you want, I'll give it to you

snippet.description:
NEW 99 Nights in the Forest PLAYLIST  🏕️ - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuj1bxPGqr_6cfY0tqBSIaR9rGcpnp9vN

A new adventure in the world of ROBLOX! Now Player must escape in 99 NIGHTS IN THE FOREST, while DEER will be behind them, do you think they can escape this and more of the hostile beasts stay to see how this chapter of ROBLOX ends.

► SUBSCRIBE to the Channel! - https://www.youtube.com/@CartoonGames-l7x

📚 WHAT IS 99 Nights in the Forest?!

This official wiki is about the Roblox game, 99 Nights in the Forest, developed by Grandma’s Favorite Games. In 99 Nights in the Forest, players have to build a camp with their friends and find and rescue the 4 missing children, whilst avoiding a vicious Deer, its Cultists, and other hostile beasts.

In 99 Nights in the Forest, players have to build a camp with their friends and find and rescue the 4 missing children, whilst avoiding a vicious Deer, its Cultists, and other hostile beasts.

snippet.description:
👊 Hey there! My name is Knoxy!

📩 media@protagames.com

snippet.title: Edge of Fate's fate was already sealed. (First Impressions)
snippet.description:
my first impressions on edge of fate are here. it's not a perfect expansion, not even close. i have my fair share of gripes about the campaign gameplay and about leveling. new foundations are being formed, plenty of new systems to tweak to get them right. but it felt like a lot of people went into the expansion hating it before it even came out and i do think the hate has gone a bit too far.

i plan on using this space to give more thoughts as i get questions/topics to discuss. if i get enough things that i wanna follow up on, i'll just make another video.

intro - 0:00
story - 0:26
campaign gameplay - 6:56
the portal/leveling - 13:59
stat revamps/new gear - 26:05
ultimately though - 31:28

snippet.title: Thanks Nintendo
snippet.description:
Nintendo just made another update patch with HUGE consequences for MKWorld. According to the patch notes, "lap-type" courses will show up more online instead of "intermission" (or route or highway) tracks. But is that really true? And why did they change how trick boosts work?
